1 Introduction

Accounting is the process of recording, classifying, and summarizing financial transactions of a business. In India, GST (Goods and Services Tax) is applied on goods and services.
This project demonstrates how accounting transactions and GST calculations are managed using Tally Prime software.
Tally Prime is widely used accounting software that helps businesses maintain financial records, manage inventory, and generate reports.

